Description: Software library containing methods for estimating age-specific 
death rates and life tables based on demographic indicators other that 
death counts and population exposure to risk. E.g. life expectancy, infant 
mortality or observed surviorship within arbitrary age intervals. The methods 
are described in Pascariu et al. (2020) <doi:10.3390/risks8040109> and 
Wilmoth et al. (2012) <doi:10.1080/00324728.2011.611411>.
